# Design System Integration Protocol - Headless Shopify

## üö® CRITICAL: NO INLINE STYLES

**ABSOLUTE RULE:** NEVER use inline `style={{}}` props. ALL styling MUST be in CSS classes in `components/components.css`.

‚ùå **FORBIDDEN:**
```typescript
<div style={{ padding: 'var(--space-xl)' }}>  // Even with tokens!
<div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: '16px' }}>
```

‚úÖ **REQUIRED:**
```typescript
<div className="ds-component-name">
```

Then add CSS:
```css
.ds-component-name {
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-md);
}
```

**Exception:** Only SVG gradient `<stop>` elements can use inline styles (CSS cannot target them).

