## Core Principle
Use self-contained React/TypeScript components with design tokens and component composition. Each component includes its own CSS styles in `components/components.css`, prefixed with `ds-`, following cursor rules. Components use TypeScript interfaces and compose reusable components from the component library. **ALL styling is done via CSS classes - NO inline styles.**

**Source of Truth:** All design tokens are defined in `app/tokens.css`. This file is imported in `app/layout.tsx` and loaded globally.

