## Component Composition Rules

### When to Create New Components

These are **guidelines**, not strict laws.

‚úÖ **Create new component when:**
- Reusable UI pattern appears 3+ times
- Complex interaction logic needed
- Standalone feature with multiple parts
- **Section Components:** Large page sections (Hero, Features) should be their own components

‚ùå **Don't create component when:**
- Used only once (inline JSX is fine for unique layouts)
- Simple HTML structure
- Better as inline JSX

**Flexibility Clause:**
For one-off unique pages (like a campaign landing page), you may compose layouts inline without creating reusable components for every section, **provided you strictly use design tokens and base components**.

